OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStormont crisis putting    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fessential services at risk 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Essential services in Northern Ireland 
OL,6, are being put at risk by the lack of a 
OL,7, Stormont budget, according to the heads
OL,8, of more than 50 public bodies.         
OL,10,FExecutive departments are expected to  
OL,11,Fface big cuts to their spending in this
OL,12,Ffinancial year when the budget is set. 
OL,14,FBut the Public Sector Chairs' Forum    
OL,15,Fsaid that initial indications that the 
OL,16,Fcuts could hit 20% were alarming.      
OL,18,FIt has written to Northern Ireland     
OL,19,FSecretary Chris Heaton-Harris, asking  
OL,20,Fhim for urgent clarity on the budget.  
